if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"又唱歌屌你老母"},{"pid":"5b9f329ea38862535369150fe8a42cbaca3e453e","tid":2003931,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da3a0176855673618b878a3a07559e6acd76b74","tid":2003931,"uid":68689,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"大家都預左 果日各區商場和你sing可能仲理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:02:14.000Z","msg":"以後有任何遊行被黑警bam就唱歌?"},{"pid":"7707cfdb19a1b612249e7bd8bf602e9b9f69c7ee","tid":2003931,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29ef94d0c4e4f47425ebbe213dd18352e88f21e0","tid":2003931,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提一提, 所謂「思頴團隊」疑似社民連人馬<br />\n遊行主題偏離全民共識五大訴求<br />\n自己決定跟唔跟</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019-12-01<br />\n民間發起今午（12月1日）「毋忘初心大遊行」，由尖沙嘴鐘樓對開空地遊行至紅館，重申五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n【19:30】發起遊行的「連登仔」Swing晚上7時許宣布，遊行有最少38萬人參與，大會本來預定在起點鐘樓、近香格里拉酒店位置及終點點算人數，但由於警方4時許強制終止遊行，所以只能點算起點及酒店對開人數，當時仍有市民加入，所以相信人數高於38萬。警方估計，高峰時有1.6萬人參與。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191201/s00001/85bc8694a0c476d2d557cff2d9d49445.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F85bc8694a0c476d2d557cff2d9d49445.jpg&h=7337df18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191201/s00001/84c1a712f88c74043b6e67b942d03e8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F84c1a712f88c74043b6e67b942d03e8a.jpg&h=b53b70e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191201/s00001/8a2863b60f57c8763d2d9bdc4a94d94a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F8a2863b60f57c8763d2d9bdc4a94d94a.jpg&h=8f4bcf6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191201/s00001/87fe5fc7c152f1ab4ba1ff75d0dd6fe2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191201%2Fs00001%2F87fe5fc7c152f1ab4ba1ff75d0dd6fe2.jpg&h=14fec70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【17:44】部分於尖沙嘴彌敦道與梳士巴利道交界的防暴警撤離，警方以揚聲器稱大會已宣布遊行結束，呼籲市民離開，否則市民或涉參與未經批准集結。另有防暴警舉藍旗不斷推進，記者及市民走入星光大道，有市民大叫<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「再退就海嚟喇喎」</span></span></strong>，其後防暴警陸續離開。"},{"pid":"0a5d7363e1c81698afbbf1da66cb2874f7b86348","tid":2003931,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"有限聚令，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b78697a53bd415459e16a597fad3f2bb3eafb63","tid":2003931,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"無不反，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人一向好乖，無不反就唔會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8704c7cd7bf0911c444f406edbc8bda140849a5","tid":2003931,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09b50bdf7fcf164355c6650aff1b2bf4be974e98","tid":2003931,"uid":47208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2da3a0176855673618b878a3a07559e6acd76b74","tid":2003931,"uid":68689,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:36:36.000Z","msg":"大家都預左 果日各區商場和你sing可能仲理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"唔知可唔可以變成18區同一日<br />\n一個場比人禁就轉另一個場"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"Why not same time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}